decks.notes: This deck focuses on aggressive strategies, utilizing low-cost creatures, burn spells, and sacrifice outlets to quickly deal damage to the opponent. The goal is to have a fast and efficient offense, overwhelming the opponent before they can establish their own game plan. By utilizing cards like Judith, the Scourge Diva, Goblin Guide, Lightning Bolt, and Demonic Tutor, the deck aims to control the board and apply consistent pressure on the opponent. Sacrifice outlets like Viscera Seer and Goblin Bombardment provide additional reach and synergy with creatures that benefit from being sacrificed. With a mix of efficient creatures, removal, and disruptive spells, this deck aims to win through consistent aggression and resource management.

This deck focuses on quickly overwhelming the opponent with aggressive creatures and burn spells, utilizing Ghyrson Starn, Kelermorph as the commander. The main goal is to apply pressure early on with cards like Goblin Guide and Monastery Swiftspear, while also utilizing efficient removal spells like Lightning Bolt and Chain Lightning to control the board. The deck also includes cards like Mana Confluence and Expressive Iteration to ensure consistent mana sources and card advantage. By maintaining a fast pace and applying constant pressure, this deck aims to defeat the opponent before they have a chance to stabilize or mount a significant defense.
